{"tid":1810652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢非典型肺炎】何栢良憂春運令武漢非典型肺炎擴散   張建宗： 　暫毋須減往來武漢航班及高鐵班次","createTime":"2020-01-04T05:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T07:03:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"63281dfd59ffcbd79e134516df724446babfac49","tid":1810652,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"以後統一正名：「武漢非典型肺炎」<br />\n廢事一陣爆到落香港, 香港社區爆發仲勁過武漢時<br />\n全世界又以為 (或屈) 香港係源頭<br />\n<br />\n==================================<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500976-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500976-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=f3011fea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500976-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=de7f8a0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500976-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良認為，有充分理由分析，武漢非典型肺炎爆發涉及新型病毒，相信當地有發生懷疑涉及人傳人的情況，病毒亦有一定的殺傷力，認為本港要當作病毒可以人傳人的情況應對。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，春運期間有機會令武漢非典型肺炎病毒進一步擴散，情況令人擔心，亦估計，如果源頭是來自野味或野生動物，會透過供應鏈傳到其他內地省市，希望內地政府有最新資訊，會盡快全面公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500981-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500981-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=a52f8e83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500981-20200104.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f12675f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500981-20200104.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗表示，政府已就武漢不明病毒性肺炎個案作出高度戒備，啟動嚴重應變級別，亦不斷與內地方面聯繫，強調不會掉以輕心，如出現爆發時可以即時回應。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，最重要是防疫把關工作及注意個人衞生，現階段無必要減少來往武漢及香港的航班及高鐵班次。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對於教育局局長楊潤雄早前接受訪問時說，如果有校長不勝任，局方可以取消他的校長資格，張建宗說，老師的質素及品行很重要，當局已清楚表明以學生福祉及教師專業為出發點，強調絕無半點針對老師，不存在白色恐怖。"},{"pid":"d32056cabc984fa06fb40d927b5474bc467be86c","tid":1810652,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5dee015a4209af2ee6305734bd52a8aab2ce6fd","tid":1810652,"uid":85578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 你班仆街高官unun 腳隨便就害到香港人咁"},{"pid":"8a54d64d8f238b85b696ee82c898f52e765b99d6","tid":1810652,"uid":55321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"減黎都冇用，有手有腳要落黎實有方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1b562d211e662931d6b5360c563c52ba48d820","tid":1810652,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5dee015a4209af2ee6305734bd52a8aab2ce6fd","tid":1810652,"uid":85578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 你班仆街高官unun 腳隨便就害到香港人咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:27:13.000Z","msg":"呢班攔坦先至係食人血饅頭"},{"pid":"60d44deda118937de4a2a7ed1155ef7121f85c49","tid":1810652,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a54d64d8f238b85b696ee82c898f52e765b99d6","tid":1810652,"uid":55321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"減黎都冇用，有手有腳要落黎實有方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:28:20.000Z","msg":"唔知聽日上水光復會否變「勇武封關」？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad56317be0f5ae4b794711f34b54274b455d8379","tid":1810652,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src